Package: robustCausalTree
Type: Package
Title: Median-based Splitting Rules for the Causal Tree
Version: 0.0.1 
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lennard", "Maßmann", email = "lennard.massmann@uni-due.de", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Karolina", "Gliszczyńska", email = "", role = "aut"))
Description: Estimating heterogeneous treatment effects using causal forests with median-based splitting rules within the causal tree.
    For more information, see Maßmann and Gliszczyńska  (2026).
    Our current package relies heavily on the 'causalTree' package and the 'htetree' package on 'GitHub'. We 
    greatly appreciate the authors for their extremely useful and free packages.
